# Election Assistant — Environment Configuration
# Copy to .env.local and fill in your values. Never commit .env.local.

# ── Required ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Google Gemini API key — required for Prototype D (AI Conversation)
# Free key: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=AIza...

# ── Optional: LLM observability (Helicone) ────────────────────────────────────
# Routes Gemini calls through Helicone's proxy for usage tracking, quota
# monitoring, and conversation logging. Leave unset to bypass (direct Gemini).
# Get a free key: https://helicone.ai → Settings → API Keys
HELICONE_API_KEY=sk-helicone-...
